                    <div data-sid="more-reviews_1" class="sie-more-reviews_1 se">
                        <p class="se-t sie-more-reviews_1-text st-m-paragraph st-d-paragraph se-rc"><i>Kendall Point is
                                a perfect mixture of modern and classy. The ceremony lawn is breathtaking along with the
                                surrounding views of the hill country. The getting ready suits are so spacious,
                                comfortable, and accommodating! The venue itself is just so amazing in a million ways.
                                Big wedding or small wedding, it is absolutely the most perfect property to fulfill your
                                wedding day dreams! 🤍<br>-Skylar M<br><br>We could not have picked a better venue than
                                Kendall Point to celebrate our special day! They were helpful at every step of the
                                planning process and made our day so easy! I highly recommend Kristin and her gorgeous
                                venue, you will not regret getting married here!<br>-Haley M<br><br>I cannot say enough
                                amazing things about Kendall Point. Kristin, the owner, was deemed my fairy godmother of
                                my fairytale wedding because she truly was instrumental in making my magical day what it
                                was. From our first tour she helped make our STUNNING venue truly the best choice for
                                us. She is one of the top, if not the top, expert in weddings in San Antonio and her
                                advice was unparalleled.&nbsp;<br>-Jimmi V<br><br>I have a hard time putting into words
                                just how AMAZING Kendall Point, Kristin and team, and my wedding day experience overall
                                was! If you have a very specific vision in mind, I want to mention- KP is a beautiful
                                white blank slate that you can really dress up or down and just transform into any
                                creation! I wanted to go over the top with floral and design and IT WAS SO BEAUTIFUL the
                                staircase (swoon!) and just grand presence of this place feels so magical. HIGHLY
                                recommend.<br>-Caitlyn Sells<br><br>The MOMENT I got engaged, there was only ONE venue
                                on my mind I just knew I had to have my wedding reception at: KP. I didn’t waste a
                                single moment looking at other venue options because this place had it ALL. The grounds,
                                the building itself, the suites for the wedding party, the stairs (gave me Beauty and
                                the Beast vibes), and the privacy of the location. The balcony for first looks. THE
                                SWING! It was a no-brainer. The vendors we all worked with who partnered with KP made
                                for such a beautiful and effortless day. The day went by so fast, but everyone made sure
                                we enjoyed ourselves. I’d get married here all over again in a heartbeat. 100000000/10,
                                KP! Well done! Love you all!<br>-Jeishka Varon<br><br>Kendall Point was my number 1
                                choice to host my wedding. The venue alone is gorgeous! Wrap around porch, the stairs to
                                head down for your ceremony— gorgeous! Lots of great spots to do pictures around the
                                venue! Kristin is amazing! Along with the vendors! Book now! She books up fast! You
                                won’t regret it!<br>-Naizeth Muniz<br><br>As a vendor experience, Kendall Point offers
                                one of the BEST wedding experiences in the industry. The owners are hands on and really
                                take of theirs clients and vendors. This venue will blown you away with so much beauty
                                in every corner, making a picture perfect for every photo. A MUST see! Highly
                                recommended for all couples who wants stellar service and unforgettable event
                                day!<br>-Grice Torres<br><br>We got married here in November 2020. Despite all the
                                challenges that this year threw at us, the unknown of whether we were going to be able
                                to have a wedding or not, we could not have been happier with Kendall Point. Kristin
                                (the owner) is the most down to earth and accommodating person! Our guests STILL tell us
                                how perfect the wedding was, how BEAUTIFUL the venue is, and how everything went off
                                without a hitch! We can't thank everyone at Kendall Point enough for everything they did
                                for us. Brides, have your wedding here - you will NOT regret it!<br>- Ashleigh
                                J.<br><br>Kendall Point is beautifully manicured and perfectly laid out for guests to
                                mingle, dance and share a fantastic time. Great picture opportunities make a super fun
                                time!<br>- Maribel G.<br><br>This breathtaking family owned and operated wedding venue
                                is hands down an excellent choice. Kristin is a saint who will make sure your wedding is
                                exactly perfect no matter what! They’re so well known in the local wedding world not
                                only for the immaculate property, but also for their extremely high customer service!
                                I’ve had the pleasure of photographing dozens of weddings here, and each one has been
                                unique and perfect in its own way, with the common theme being total organization and
                                ease due to the exceptional vendor list the owners hand picked, and every tiny last
                                detail on the property being clean and lovely for each couple on their wedding day. I
                                cannot say enough good about this place!<br>- Annakyi G.<br><br>I don’t even know where
                                to begin when talking about how great Kendall Point is as a venue! Not only is this
                                venue wonderful, but Kristin and her team made our day one that we will cherish forever!
                                Booking a wedding date before the pandemic started and then having to plan during a
                                pandemic not really knowing what was going to happen was extremely stressful! However,
                                Kristin took away away all that stress with her professionalism, kindness, and
                                flexibility. They took every precaution to make our guests feel safe! Just a small
                                example of how great the venue and Kristin is: After our ceremony we were going to take
                                photos and my feet were hurting so I took off my heels, however I was apprehensive about
                                walking in the grass barefoot. With no hesitation Kristin kicked off her shoes and let
                                me wear them as we took our scenic photos (which was a good 20-30 minutes)! If you are
                                looking for a venue where you want to feel warmth, kindness, and love this is the place
                                for you! We love Kendall!!<br>- Nina M.<br><br>My wedding was originally planned for
                                March 20th - but then the COVID shut down happened just FOUR days prior. Everything was
                                in place; all the details were done and vendors were payed. But as any 2020 bride knows,
                                we didn’t get a choice and there was nothing we could do.<br>Thankfully, I was a Kendall
                                bride which means you get Kristin on your side. She was so compassionate through those
                                heartbreaking days. She immediately helped me pick a new date in August, while brides
                                with other venues were being told they were just out of luck and would have to pay
                                everything again if they wanted a new date. We still got married in a tiny ceremony in
                                my parents backyard, and I was very skeptical that my second “wedding” would feel like
                                what I’d always dreamed of. Thankfully I was completely wrong! You can see for yourself
                                the incredible beauty of the venue. The staircases are truly magnificent and the bridal
                                suite is one of my favorite places of all time. But the thing that made the difference
                                to me was how supportive Kristin was in the midst of the storm, and how she really cared
                                about what I was going through. I knew she was on my side through it all and was working
                                as hard as anyone could to make sure my day happened as I’d envisioned it. I could text
                                her with questions or concerns and she was always so quick to answer them. When our DJ
                                discovered a conflict at the last minute and was going to send us a substitute, she was
                                on top of it and figured out a solution to where everything went as planned. Setting up
                                and tearing down are so easy here with the amazing team that they have in place. I can’t
                                imagine having had my wedding anywhere else - the day was absolutely perfect!<br>- Lydia
                                G.<br><br>If you’re looking for a wedding venue in the Boerne area, look no further
                                Kendall Point is your place! This stunning venue offers everything needed to have your
                                extraordinary dream day. Kristin and her family go above and beyond to accommodate all
                                of your wedding wants, no matter what your style. Not only is it the most beautiful
                                place equipped with everything needed to have the most perfect wedding, they provided a
                                great list of photographers, florists, D.J.’s, bartenders and food vendors. Thank you
                                for an amazing day enjoyed by all!<br>- Kim R.<br><br>Fabulous wedding venue! Fantastic
                                owner! One of the main reasons we chose Kendall Point initially was because of the
                                beauty of the venue inside and out, but when we met Kristin Voss, we knew we had to book
                                Kendall Point! Kristin is extremely knowledgeable and helpful! We couldn't have asked
                                for better service whenever we called with a question, and we were provided with a list
                                of top-notch vendors at our initial meeting, so we were able to make plans immediately.
                                Our daughter's wedding was a breeze to plan from start to finish because of Kristin Voss
                                and the vendors she helped us choose. We had fun on the wedding day because Kristin and
                                our planner had taken care of every detail! Kristin made herself available to us
                                whenever we needed her, and she had everything set and ready for our vendors when we
                                arrived. I cannot say enough good things about Kendall Point. The venue was beautiful
                                before we ever brought in any flowers, so we didn't have to do much to the wedding site
                                or to the reception area. All of the guests who came to the wedding and reception have
                                told us what an amazing time they had and how stunning the location was! We couldn't
                                have been happier with our choice!<br>- Margy P.<br><br>When I saw Kendall Point for the
                                first time on the Knot, I knew I wanted to have my wedding there! It is simply the most
                                gorgeous wedding venue and it was exactly what I was looking for. The owner, Kristin, is
                                very sweet and helpful. Our wedding day (Dec. 15. 2017) went SO smoothly and perfectly,
                                the guests are raving about how beautiful Kendall Point was. I chose all of my vendors
                                from their list and every single vendor was extremely professional to work with and an
                                absolute joy. Also, at Kendall, they have a stunning bride &amp; groom suite to get
                                ready in which was perfect for my girls and for my husband’s groomsmen. The entire venue
                                is a dream and if you are still searching for a venue, LOOK NO FURTHER! Kendall is the
                                best choice. I am so thankful I had my wedding here and will cherish the memories made
                                in this venue.<br>- Anais H.<br><br><a href="san-antonio-wedding-venue.html"
